title: NTP Ep. 1 - If I were your enemy.
description:
Are you trying your best to measure up - yet you still feel as if you're not enough? Let's start here. You can be free from pressure, you can admit your greatest needs, you can make it your greatest goal to know and love Jesus.

Download the Nothing to Prove book club kit: jennieallen.com

Find the Nothing to Prove book: https://www.amazon.com/Nothing-Prove-Stop-Trying-Hard/dp/1601429614

Find the Nothing to Prove Bible study guide: https://www.amazon.com/Nothing-Prove-Study-Guide-Streaming-ebook/dp/B08ZMF8QFJ
